select column_name as `column_name` from information_schema.columns where table_schema = 'wabizz1_app' and table_name = 'roles'

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` = 88 and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\User'
select count(*) as aggregate from `orders` where `created_at` > '2021-11-26 13:05:46' and `orders`.`deleted_at` is null and `restorant_id` = 69

select ROUND(SUM(order_price+delivery_price),2) as order_price, SUM(delivery_price + static_fee + fee_value) AS total_fee, SUM(delivery_price) AS total_delivery, SUM(static_fee) AS total_static_fee, SUM(fee_value) AS total_fee_value from `orders` where `created_at` > '2021-11-26 13:05:46' and `payment_status` = 'paid' and `orders`.`deleted_at` is null and `restorant_id` = 69 limit 1

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null and `status_id` = 5

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` is null order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1

select * from `tables` where `tables`.`id` is null and `tables`.`id` is not null

select count(id) as totalPerMonth, ROUND(SUM(order_price + delivery_price),2) AS sumValue, MONTH(created_at) month from `orders` where `created_at` > '2021-06-01 00:00:00' and `payment_status` = 'paid' and `orders`.`deleted_at` is null and `restorant_id` = 69 group by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) order by YEAR(created_at), MONTH(created_at) asc
select * from `companies` where `companies`.`user_id` = 88 and `companies`.`user_id` is not null and `companies`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
